{
  "text": "The relevance of monotonicity in the context of epistemic analysis of finite strategic games has already been pointed out in [CITATION_1] , where the connection is also noted between the iterated elimination of non-optimal strategies and the calculation of the fixpoint of the corresponding operator.",
  "citation_candidates": [
